  m_Name: "Level_02_Dzibilchalt\xFAn"
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  levelNumber: 2
  levelName: "Dzibilchalt\xFAn"
  location: Yucatan, Mexico
  levelDescription: "Ancient even among the Maya, Dzibilchalt\xFAn was a city of
    scholars and traders.\nIts famous Temple of the Seven Dolls aligns perfectly
    with the sunrise on the equinox, flooding its doorways with light.\n\nThe site
    thrived for over 2,000 years, linking the coast to inland cities through salt
    and obsidian trade.\nIts cenote, a natural well, offered life-giving water and
    a sacred link to the underworld.\n\nThough later absorbed by Spanish colonial
    influence, the city\u2019s stones still whisper of ceremony, learning, and cosmic
    order.\nWhen the sun passes through the temple\u2019s eyes, the ancient day begins
    anew."
  requiredStackHeight: 15
  oneStarScore: 200
  twoStarScore: 600
  threeStarScore: 1000
  swingSpeedMultiplier: 1.2
  swingAmplitudeMultiplier: 1.1
